data.name: openPowerShellToolStripMenuItem.ToolTipText
data.value: Opens a PowerShell console with current site collection pre-loaded. This enables quick access to the site collection with PowerShell based on Client Side Object Model (CSOM). Only available via adding Site Collection below "Sites"-node, not via Office 365 Tenant.
